 D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.55</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: c. dat. loci, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0081.tlg001:3:64\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.64</biblScope> </bibl> (nisi leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">[ἐν] χωρίοις</foreign>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">; λοχίσαντος</foreign> is prob. l. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg066:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Oth.\">Oth.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n63987.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">beset with an ambuscade</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λελοχισμένον χωρίον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0081.tlg001:1:79\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.79</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n63987.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">distribute men in companies</tr_> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">λόχοι</etym>), and so, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">put them in order of battle</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:103\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.103</biblScope></bibl>, Aen. Tact.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.5</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg033:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <t